data.text:
Welcome to the Rural Municipality of Prince Albert NO. 461, one of the larger municipalities in the province. It is our pleasure to introduce you to our community.

The RM is a diverse municipality composed of agricultural land, commercial and industrial developments, country residential properties, golf courses and forest areas.

The quality of life is wonderful in our community and we look forward to you discovering the reasons to live, work and play in the Rural Municipality of Prince Albert No. 461.

The RM of Prince Albert is nestled between the north and south Saskatchewan River and is located south of Prince Albert. The boundaries of the RM stretch east to the river forks and west to the third Meridian.
